<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>my Portfolio</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
         :root {
            --gold: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #f5e6a8);
            --dark: #0b0b0e;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #111, #000);
            color: white;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            background: var(--gold);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: fadeDown 1.5s ease;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: fadeUp 2s ease;
        }
        
        .scroll {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        
        .section {
            padding: 120px 10%;
        }
        
        .glass {
            background: var(--glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 60px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }
        
        .about h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .about p {
            line-height: 1.9;
            opacity: 0.85;
        }
        
        .skills {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }
        
        .skill {
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
            transition: transform 0.5s;
        }
        
        .skill:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .projects {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .project {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        
        .project img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.7s;
        }
        
        .project:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.15);
        }
        
        .project span {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .contact {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .contact a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            background: var(--gold);
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.4s;
        }
        
        .contact a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        footer {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-40px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(40px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="hero">
        <div>
            <h1>Shweta Samgir</h1>
            <p>web Designer • Creative Developer • programmer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll">▼ Scroll</div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="glass about">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>
                I create premium digital experiences that combine elegance, innovation, and performance. My work focuses on luxury aesthetics, cinematic motion, and unforgettable brand identity.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="glass">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom:40px;">Expertise</h2>
            <div class="skills">
                <div class="skill">web Design</div>
                <div class="skill">Creative Development</div>
                <div class="skill">Brand Identity</div>
                <div class="skill">Motion & Interaction</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="glass">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom:40px;">Selected Work</h2>
            <div class="projects">
                <div class="project">
                    <img src="https://resources.americaneagle.com/aecom-blobs/images/default-source/blog-images/understanding-web-development-frameworks-og-image.jpg?sfvrsn=d289bf2d_1" alt="">
                    <span>web designer</span>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f" alt="">
                    <span>Creative Studio</span>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085" alt="">
                    <span>Digital Experience</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="glass contact">
            <h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
            <p>High-end ideas deserve high-end execution.</p>
            <a href="shwetasamgie05@example.com">Contact Me</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        © 2025 Your Name — Crafted with elegance
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
